 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=izudin>Izudin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 106<br> <font color=#333333>(9/15/02 8:40:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1532.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Yes</span><hr size=1> Yes, you can buy at least one pet spell for every spell circle past 16 (where research starts), up to 49. These pets are sold together with the normal spells at your local mage guild.<br>
<br>
There are supposedly some more pet spells for higher level pets sold in Katta, but I havent been there to check this out myself.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ugaladwynxev.showPublicProfile?language=EN>GaladwynXev</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#333333>(9/15/02 9:00:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1532.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://image1ex.villagephotos.com/pubimage.asp?id_=570233  WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Yes</span><hr size=1> Sweet. I am so glad to hear that. I tried doing research and it was so frustrating that I nearly wanted to quit. Right now I have decided to just look for components every now and again and up my skill through the guild. I wasted too much time and money, and I would much rather have fun with this game, then to quit just because of research. Sorry to ramble on and thanks for the info.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umurgson.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Murgson</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(9/15/02 11:01:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1532.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Yes</span><hr size=1> You can get all the 44 (and 39 I think, but I was past that when I went there) pet spells in Katta Castelum, you have to click on the banners in the guild hall to get to get to